rows.label: qst104227_msg0001
rows.name:
Alright, I'm going to do some actual
salvaging now, so watch closely.

rows.label: qst104227_msg0002
rows.name:
You guys don't have salvaging
gear yet, so you can't do
it today, but...

rows.label: qst104227_msg0003
rows.name:
...watching it up close
will help you not be nervous
when it's your turn.

rows.label: qst104227_msg0004
rows.name:
This is the first time I've
seen salvaging up close...

rows.label: qst104227_msg0005
rows.name:
Isn't the cylinder heavy?
Won't you just sink?

rows.label: qst104227_msg0006
rows.name:
Rex-sensei! We're waiting
for the treasure!

rows.label: qst104227_msg0007
rows.name: You got it! Leave it to me!
